headline: Paychex, Inc. Schedules First Quarter Fiscal 2026 Earnings Conference Call for September 30, 2025
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., September 16, 2025--Paychex, Inc. (Nasdaq: PAYX), an industry-leading human capital management ("HCM") company, will release financial results for its fiscal 2026 first quarter ended August 31, 2025 before the financial markets open on Tuesday, September 30, 2025.
